config BR2_PACKAGE_THINGINO_PROVISION
	bool "thingino-provision"
	help
	  Thingino Provisioning System

	  This package provides an automated provisioning system for Thingino devices.
	  It allows devices to fetch configuration from a provisioning server based on
	  their MAC address, featuring secure authentication.

	  Features:
	  - Device-specific configuration based on MAC address
	  - Secure authentication with salted password hashes
	  - Support for UENV, SYSTEM, and USER configuration sections
	  - DHCP-triggered provisioning support
